				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Skull of Vellioth, former Cazador's master. He wants you to stop Cazador. He shows you fragments of his memories about Cazador. Succeeding on several checks during the dialog will give you an edge against Cazador in the final confrontation.\r\nAt the end the skull releases its jaw and get the scroll. NOTE Please set the display name of the skull to Vellioth."
				}
